http://IRockJazz.com IRockJazz caught Kenny Barron in Chicago, and we discussed the trends in Modern Jazz, and how the music has taken a turn towards the intellectual technique, and away from the heart, and how that impacts the memorability of the music by the audience.

Interested seeing more great interviews? Visit www.irockjazz.com
